The paper deals with text modelling techniques and proposes a generative log-linear model for learning document embeddings along with their uncertainties. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of Natural Language Processing (NLP) which falls under cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper also addresses the problem of intractability during variational inference, which is a common issue in machine learning and optimization. This suggests that the paper may also belong to the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Computer Vision (cs.CV), and Information Retrieval (cs.IR).
